# Simple Mapping App

This is a lightweight and easy-to-use mapping application that allows you to visualize data points on a map. You can adjust the map's size and the color of the data points, making it highly customizable for your needs.

## Key Features:
- **Customizable Size:** Easily adjust the size of the map to suit your visualization needs.
- **Adjustable Colors:** Change the color of the data points for better clarity or aesthetics.

## Installation

No installation required! Simply download the script and run it without needing to install Python or any dependencies.
